author: Murray Brewster
title: Canadian military intelligence unit issued warning about Wuhan outbreak back in January
description: A small, specialized unit within the Canadian military's intelligence branch began producing detailed warnings and analysis about the emergence of the deadly novel coronavirus in Wuhan, China in early January, CBC News has learned.
content:
